Further Details:
Jupiter is home to a number of Prisons and detention centres all of which are based in floating platforms floating on to just below the surface of the planet, with the higEarth security one being located a full mile under the surface in the centre of the planets famous giant red spot storm only coming up to exchange prisoners or to take on supplies.
